"Just Shoe It" Items appraised include a 2006 Dutch Arnold & Son Longitude II watch; a collection of vintage handcuffs; and an original 1944 panoramic photo of Las Vegas Army Air Field. Also, after Rick promises Chumlee 2% of profits on large deals on items in which Chumlee is knowledgeable, Chumlee takes Rick to ShoeZeum, a museum billed as the world's largest collection of Nike sneakers, which is for sale.
